  "title": "Admin Assistant / Clerk (Warehouse) #77236",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Toy Distributor</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Admin Assistant / Clerk (Warehouse)</strong></li><li>Working Location: East – Macpherson</li><li>Working Hours: 5 Days / Mon – Fri: 8.30am – 6pm</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>SGD 1600 + Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Move and organize toy boxes (items are light and easy to handle)</li><li>Check returned goods and verify quantity and condition</li><li>Enter return details into the computer system</li><li>Repack items into boxes and apply labels</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Comfortable using computers for routine tasks</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#77236 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
